thread.title_full: Prep football: Mike Helfgot's Week 5 Top 20 - Chicago Tribune

author: Mike Helfgot
title: Prep Mike Helfgot's Week 5 Top 20
text:
1. Homewood-Flossmoor 4-0 (Last week: 1)
Defeated Joliet Central 60-0.
Next: Friday at Lockport.
2. Loyola 4-0 (2)
Defeated Fenwick 54-16.
Next: Saturday vs. St. Ignatius.
3. Mount Carmel 4-0 (3)
Defeated St. Rita 35-14.
Next: Friday at De La Salle.
4. Glenbard West 4-0 (4)
Defeated Downers Grove North 41-0.
Next: Saturday at Lyons.
5. Montini 4-0 (6)
Defeated De La Salle 38-0.
Next: Friday at Leo.
6. Joliet Catholic 4-0 (7)
Defeated St. Viator 48-0.
Next: Friday vs. Marian Central.
7. Phillips 4-0 (8)
Defeated Julian 40-0.
Next: Friday vs. Vocational.
8. Stevenson 3-1 (9)
Defeated Wauconda 20-7.
Next: Friday vs. Libertyville.
9. Libertyville 4-0 (10)
Defeated Lake Forest 42-7.
Next: Friday at Stevenson.
10. Hinsdale Central 4-0 (14)
Defeated York 52-21.
Next: Saturday vs. Proviso West.
11. Barrington 4-0 (12)
Defeated Wheeling 42-21.
Next: Friday at Schaumburg.
12. Oak Park 4-0 (13)
Defeated Proviso West 41-0.
Next: Friday vs. Downers Grove North.
13. Lincoln-Way East 3-1 (15)
Defeated Stagg 50-0.
Next: Friday at Bolingbrook.
14. Marian Central 4-0 (NR)
Defeated Nazareth 34-19.
Next: Friday at Joliet Catholic.
15. Nazareth 3-1 (12)
Lost to Marian Central 34-19.
Next: Friday vs. Marian Catholic.
16. Brother Rice 3-1 (18)
Defeated St. Francis 46-33.
Next: Friday at St. Laurence.
17. Neuqua Valley 3-1 (17)
Defeated Wheaton Warrenville South 28-14.
Next: Friday at Bartlett.
18. Marist 3-1 (NR)
Defeated Notre Dame 49-42.
Next: Friday at Benet.
19. Simeon 2-2 (19)
Defeated Lane 56-0.
Next: Friday vs. Curie.
20. Batavia 4-0 (20)
Defeated St. Charles East 28-0.
Next: Friday at St. Charles North.
On the verge: Cary-Grove 4-0, Geneva 4-0, Lincoln-Way West 4-0, Notre Dame 3-1, New Trier 4-0.
Mike Helfgot is a freelance reporter for the Chicago Tribune.
